blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary: Cosevee Cosmog and Eevee fusion Psychic/Normal Type Ability: Cute Charm/Unaware. Hidden Ability: Adaptability Stats: HP - 60,...
caption:
Cosevee

Cosmog and Eevee fusion

Psychic/Normal Type

Ability: Cute Charm/Unaware.

Hidden Ability: Adaptability

Stats: HP - 60, Atk - 45, Def - 45, SpA - 40, SpD - 50, Spe - 50

The Space Dust Pokemon

Cosevee flies through space, exploring and discovering new and exciting things. Different planets and stars can induce a mutation in Cosevee. Many consider its sighting as rare as a shooting star.

I’ve seen many people make their own Cosmog/Eevee fusion and wanted to have a go. What a cute little boy! He reminds me of nyan cat for some reason.

summary: (9/11/18) The Pokémon marathon on Twitch is now LIVE! There are going to be 10 episodes that is going to be streamed (from...
body:
(9/11/18) The Pokémon marathon on Twitch is now LIVE!

There are going to be 10 episodes that is going to be streamed (from Season 3 The Johto Journeys) for today’s marathon! It will feature Jessie’s past of going to a nursing school for Chansey, Ash’s first Johto gym battle with Falkner, the episode where they first visit the Charicific Valley :’( and more!

The episode set will rerun in multiple times today just so you won’t miss the stream depending on your schedule.

Watching with Twitch chat could be the best (or worst) experience you’ll ever have! But if you want a more comfy chat experience, feel free to talk/chat about the marathon in my Pokémon Discord server PokéTōku —> Invite link here :)
